Rock, paper, scissors!

325
00:38:22,900 --> 00:38:24,390
Ok, Mao's "it"!

326
00:38:26,337 --> 00:38:31,070
One... two... three...

327
00:38:32,943 --> 00:38:34,035
four...

328
00:38:34,245 --> 00:38:35,439
Hey, can I...

329
00:38:36,947 --> 00:38:40,849
This is our spot. Hide over there.

330
00:38:56,100 --> 00:38:58,000
I'm ready!

331
