461
00:58:27,637 --> 00:58:29,161
Ikuko?

462
00:58:36,012 --> 00:58:37,707
Ikuko!

463
00:59:21,691 --> 00:59:25,058
Shoji and Mitsuko Kawai

464
00:59:26,129 --> 00:59:29,428
Mitsuko Kawai...

