This water tank is exposedto light
from all around.

531
01:04:46,115 --> 01:04:50,518
So if something passed
in front of the light,

532
01:04:50,586 --> 01:04:53,316
it would cast a shadow on the tank.

533
01:04:53,990 --> 01:04:59,428
